Popular in Talks to sell Asset Management Arm, Confidencial Says

-- B y   S h a r o n   S m y t h
-- 
2011-02-17T07:13:41Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-02-17/popular-in-talks-to-sell-asset-management-arm-confidencial-says.html
  Banco Popular Espanol SA  is in talks
to sell 60 percent of its asset management division to  Allianz
SE , El Confidencial reported on its website.  Popular is in “very advanced talks” to sell the
controlling stake in the unit which manages 10.7 billion euros,
El Confidencial said, citing unidentified people with knowledge
of the talks.  Click here for web link  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
